# DESCRIPTION
# Determine the domain and range of f(x) = sqrt(A^2 - x^2)
#
# ENDDESCRIPTION
## DBsubject(Algebra)
## DBchapter(Functions)
## DBsection(Domain and range)
## Institution(John Wiley & Sons)
